summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting a Governor's Deed to portions of Harvard Avenue North, East Boston Street, East Lynn Street and Miller Street and accepting portions of Block 2, H. C. Pettit Addition, Block 2 Miller's First Addition and portions of Block 1, Peavey's First Addition for street purposes and for General Corporation purposes and authorizing the deeding of the General Corporate property to the State of Washington. (Harvard-Miller Frontage Road)
